text:
Let's be honest - I couldn't be more nostalgic about DKC2, it's my favourite game together with OoT since back then when it got released! Still, after spending 40-50 hours with DKCTF when it got released in 2014 (played it three times in a row, even once hard mode, though that was not a good idea xD ), I had to be honest to myself - that game is better than DKC2! It is so creative and polished, and there is a technical advance of about 20 years compared to the old trilogy! They couldn't do levels like that back then and though the ones from DKC2 are awesome, the ones from DKC5 just surpass them in many ways imo - the amount of detail and the endless creative ideas make it not only the best DKC game, but also the best 2D JNR ever imo. 
Though DKC2 still stays my favourite because of this huge nostalgic memories I have with it. ;) But Retro Studios have done an awesome job and I hope there will be new DKC games in the future...wouldn't mind a new 3D DK either.
